column5: Wondering what Hwy 502 between Ft Francis and Dryden is like this spring. Which part of it is rough going this year?

Rhinehart Monkey, Was on 502 the first week of this month and in my opinion in the best condition since my first trip in '80. Approx. 70 miles north is a section about 15 miles long that could use some attention, but otherwise smooth sailing!
[font color=green size=3][b]I've made two trips up 502 this spring, it's got one 22K strech that is rough, the rest was resurfaced a couple of years ago.
